casebody.data:
Sanford et al., Respondents, v. McDonald et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. September 21, 1889.)

Argued before Learned, P. J., and Landon and Putnam, JJ.

No opinion. Motion for leave to go to court of appeals denied. For former report, see 6 N. Y. Supp. 613.
